R1)
en
conf t
ip route 172.16.2.0 255.255.255.255.0 s0/0/0
ip route 172.16.3.0 255.255.255.255.0 s0/0/0

R2)
en
conf t
ip route 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.0 s0/0/0
ip route 172.16.2.0 255.255.255.255.0 s0/0/1
ip route 172.16.3.0 255.255.255.255.0 f0/0

R3)
en
conf t
ip route 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.255.0 s0/0/1
ip route 172.16.3.0 255.255.255.255.0 s0/0/1

R4)
en
conf t
ip route 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.255.0 f0/0
ip route 172.16.2.0 255.255.255.255.0 f0/0


R1 : 172.16.4.0/24
R2 : 192.168.2.0/24
       172.16.4.0/24
R3 : 192.168.2.0/24
R4 : 172.16.4.0/24
       192.168.2.0/24
추가

R1)
en
conf t
no ip route 172.16.2.0 255.255.255.0 s0/0/0
no ip route 172.16.3.0 255.255.255.0 s0/0/0
no ip route 172.16.4.0 255.255.255.0 s0/0/0

ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 s0/0/0

R1)
no ip route 주소
router rip
network 192.168.1.0
network 192.168.2.0
network 2.0.0.0

R2)
router rip
network 2.0.0.0

R3)
router rip
network 172.16.0.0
network 2.0.0.0

R4)
router rip
network 172.16.0.0
network 2.0.0.0
여기까지 하면 갔다가 안갔다가 번갈아 가면서 통신함 그 이유가 172.16.0.0/16으로 보내서
 172.16.2.0이건 172.16.3.0이건 모두 같다고 판단해서 번갈아가면서 정보를 받아서 그럼

--------------------------------
R1,2,3,4)
router rip
version 2 => RIPv2로 변경
no auto-summary => 자동축약 비활성화

이렇게 하면 위에 번갈아가면서 통신했던게 다시 정상적으로 통신함
